            "value": "<p><em>You have a special reserve of energy reserved for bursts of powerful magic.</em></p><p><strong>No Action Cost</strong> - Self - 1/Short Rest</p><p>On this turn, you can take one additional action or bonus action which can only be used to cast a spell. You also ignore the normal restrictions on the number of spells you can case in one turn, meaning you can cast a spell of @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-rules.JournalEntry.vaLYevRxKe8mAvdE.JournalEntryPage.MNWLud81msaiZukw#1st-level]{1st level} or higher with this extra action, your normal action, and your bonus action this turn if desired.</p>",
